程序包 uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.RestWebControllers

类 DeleteController

java.lang.Object
uestc.zhanghanwen.ATTCK.RestWebControllers.DeleteController
@RestController @CrossOrigin(origins="*") @RequestMapping(value="/delete", method={GET,POST}, produces="application/json;charset=UTF-8") public class DeleteController extends Object
The RESTful controller class for all creating queries.
The root URL path for this controller is domain-name/create/.
The services are deleteObjectAndRelationship(java.lang.String) and deleteRelationship(java.lang.String, java.lang.String).
